title: Super Staying Lip Stain - Zinnia brown berry - Morpho Cosmetics - Long Lasting Lip Stain
description: Water based, non drying lip stain that beautifully defines your lips without bleeding. The photo of the tube with the wand is actually our Papillon Super Staying Lip Gloss, not our Super Staying Lip Stain Zinnia, it is just an example photo of what the wand looks like in the lip stain as well. Zinnia is a natural brown berry color. It can be applied lighter for a more sheer look.

title: Olay Definity Illuminating Eye Treatment Skin Care, 0.5 Ounce
description: Olay Definity Eye Illuminator penetrates multiple surface layers and helps restore a look that’s highly defined – truly luminous. It’s dual action formula: Illuminates the complete eye area and smoothes the look of fine lines and wrinkles with a spiral of concentrated serum and strengthens delicate eye skin; firming skin’s outer layers due to a hydrating; intensive clear gel containing essential glucosamine complex. Notice immediately brighter; smoother eyes. Darkness and shadows diminish and eyes appear more luminous.
